title: Smart Digital Thermal Bottle
description: Keep your beverages hot or cold for up to 6 hours with advanced insulation. The built-in digital display shows the temperature in Celsius at a glance.

title: Camera Wall clock
description: Add style and function to any space with our 10" Modern Wall Clock. Available in black or white frames with matching or contrasting hands, it features a durable plexiglass face and a sleek 1.75" profile. Easy to hang with the built-in hook and powered by a single AA battery (included), it's the perfect timekeeping accent for any room.
